[[File:MushroomMardiGrasFestival.jpg|thumb|right|300px|The Mushroom Mardi Gras Festival in Morgan Hill, California]] A '''mushroom festival''' is a [[food festival]] in which [[mushroom]]s are featured. There are numerous mushroom festivals held annually in [[Telluride, Colorado]]; [[Kennett Square, Pennsylvania]];<ref name="visitphilly">{{cite web|url=http://www.visitphilly.com/events/philadelphia/kennett-square-mushroom-festival/|title=Kennett Square Mushroom Festival|year=2013|publisher=Greater Philadelphia Tourism Marketing Corporation|accessdate=17 February 2013}}</ref> Morel Mushroom Festival held in [[Harrison, Michigan]] and [[Boyne City, Michigan]], the [http://www.fantasticforage.com Fantastic Forage Mushroom Festival] held in Laconia, NH, and the [[Mushroom Mardi Gras Festival]] held in [[Morgan Hill, California]], Lacey, Washington
