'''[[The Breeders]]' 2017 tour''' consisted of twenty-one concerts in Europe and the United States. A date in Dublin was canceled due to [[Hurricane Ophelia (2017)|Hurricane Orphelia]].<ref>{{harvnb|The Breeders' gig at Vicar Street has been cancelled, Zara Larsson at the Olympia postponed}}</ref> They opened for [[Arcade Fire]] at two of the dates.<ref name=dates>{{harvnb|The Breeders: New Single ‘Wait in the Car’ & European & US Tour Dates}}</ref> Compositions that the Breeders played on the tour included their 2018 single "[[Wait in the Car]]", [[Pixies|the Pixies]]' "[[Gigantic (song)|Gigantic]]", and songs by [[the Amps]].<ref>{{harvnb|Blackcondorguy|2017}}</ref>
